++ Task Externalisation

TE is where existence of ongoing [Tasks] have [Externalisation]. This aids OrganisationArchitecture, MatchMaking and [Chat] as it allows [Users] to tell others what they are doing.

Examples include:
    * [Games]
    * Audio - artist
    * [Browser] - favicons

[Users] must provide [Permissions] for the tasks that have externalisation. Settings of TE is likely to appear in the TitleBar.
    * StandardRepresentations are likely to be used to present such information.